<paragraph id="E35B9301FFD4AC76F15E270DFC23FD33" blockId="7.[340,1249,562,672]" pageId="7">
D e s c r i p t i o n: Small species, 
<quantity id="241C3EE4FFD4AC76F2DF270CFCC8FDDB" box="[725,844,562,584]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.35" metricValueMax="2.6" metricValueMin="2.1" pageId="7" unit="mm" value="2.35" valueMax="2.6" valueMin="2.1">2.1-2.6 mm</quantity>
(abdomen fully extended). Coloration: forebody yellowish red to reddish brown; abdomen reddish brown to brown, with segment 
<collectionCode id="85F50BC4FFD4AC76F1842750FE2DFD10" box="[398,425,622,643]" country="Norway" name="Mykotektet, National Veterinary Institute" pageId="7">VI</collectionCode>
and the anterior half of segment 
<collectionCode id="85F50BC4FFD4AC76F2F72750FCA4FD10" box="[765,800,622,643]" pageId="7">VII</collectionCode>
infuscate; legs testaceous; antennae rufous, with the basal 2-3 antennomeres yellowish to pale reddish.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="E35B9301FFD4AC76F15E2791FD52FC93" blockId="7.[340,1248,687,768]" pageId="7">
Facies as in 
<figureCitation id="7BDF8F84FFD4AC76F1D82791FD99FD56" box="[466,541,687,709]" captionStart="Figs 20-29" captionStartId="7.[340,380,1710,1730]" captionTargetBox="[340,1248,785,1680]" captionTargetId="figure-147@7.[340,1253,1208,1685]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="Figs 20-29: Geostiba solodovnikovi sp.n. (20-23: holotype): (20) habitus; (21) head in lateral view; (22) pronotum and elytra; (23) anterior part of abdomen; (24) abdominal segment VII in lateral view; (25) tergite VII in antero-dorsal view; (26) sternite VIII; (27) median lobe of aedeagus in lateral view; (28) sternite VIII; (29) spermatheca. Scale bars: 20: 1.0 mm; 21-26, 28: 0.2 mm; 27, 29: 0.1 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5434902" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5434902/files/figure.png" pageId="7">Fig. 20</figureCitation>
. Head and pronotum with shallow fine microreticulation. Eyes small, not protruding from lateral outline of head, approximately one third the length of postocular region in dorsal view (
<figureCitation id="7BDF8F84FFD4AC76F27427D4FD4EFC93" box="[638,714,746,768]" captionStart="Figs 20-29" captionStartId="7.[340,380,1710,1730]" captionTargetBox="[340,1248,785,1680]" captionTargetId="figure-147@7.[340,1253,1208,1685]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="Figs 20-29: Geostiba solodovnikovi sp.n. (20-23: holotype): (20) habitus; (21) head in lateral view; (22) pronotum and elytra; (23) anterior part of abdomen; (24) abdominal segment VII in lateral view; (25) tergite VII in antero-dorsal view; (26) sternite VIII; (27) median lobe of aedeagus in lateral view; (28) sternite VIII; (29) spermatheca. Scale bars: 20: 1.0 mm; 21-26, 28: 0.2 mm; 27, 29: 0.1 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5434902" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5434902/files/figure.png" pageId="7">Fig. 21</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
<caption id="B79BC389FFD4AC76F15E2390FDDEF88E" ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5434902" ID-Zenodo-Dep="5434902" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5434902/files/figure.png" pageId="7" startId="7.[340,380,1710,1730]" targetBox="[340,1248,785,1680]" targetPageId="7">
<paragraph id="E35B9301FFD4AC76F15E2390FDDEF88E" blockId="7.[340,1248,1710,1821]" pageId="7">
<emphasis id="D1904F13FFD4AC76F15E2390FE3EF951" bold="true" box="[340,442,1710,1730]" pageId="7">Figs 20-29</emphasis>
: 
<taxonomicName id="24E4E882FFD4AC76F1C32390FD26F951" authority="Homson, 1974" authorityName="Homson" authorityYear="1974" box="[457,674,1710,1730]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Geostiba" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="7" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="solodovnikovi" status="sp.n.">
