) head in lateral view; (
<emphasis id="D1904F13FFD4AC76F19C23FAFE29F94B" bold="true" box="[406,429,1732,1752]" pageId="7">22</emphasis>
) pronotum and elytra; (
<emphasis id="D1904F13FFD4AC76F2A023FAFD45F94B" bold="true" box="[682,705,1732,1752]" pageId="7">23</emphasis>
) anterior part of abdomen; (
<emphasis id="D1904F13FFD4AC76F3E023FAFB85F94B" bold="true" box="[1002,1025,1732,1752]" pageId="7">24</emphasis>
